p.strong: Shape: [batch, num_heads, seq_len, d_k] per layer

div.p: At generation step t, cache contains projections for all previous tokens:
K_cache.shape = [batch, num_heads, t, d_k] V_cache.shape = [batch, num_heads, t, d_v]
Memory cost: O(L n_layers 2 batch heads seq_len d_k)
For Llama-2-70B: ~2MB per token per batch element
new_k = W_K(new_token) # [B,H,1,d_k] new_v = W_V(new_token) # [B,H,1,d_v] K_cache = cat([K_cache, new_k], dim=2) V_cache = cat([V_cache, new_v], dim=2)

[batch, heads, seq_len, d_k]
batch: 1-32 (typical) heads: 8-16 seq_len: grows +1/gen d_k: 64 (d_model/heads)

[batch, heads, seq_len, d_v]
Same shape as K d_v = d_k typically Pre-computed projections
